## One-time / infrastructure (keep in .secrets.local only)

Do **not** duplicate API tokens here unless this file stays strictly local:

- `BOOTSTRAP_TOKEN` — Worker bootstrap / super-admin upgrade
- `JWT_SECRET` — Worker JWT signing
- `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN` — deploy scripts only

See `.secrets.local.example` for the full list.

---

## Setup checklist (new environment)

1. Copy `.secrets.local.example` → `.secrets.local`
2. `npm run deploy:worker` then `npm run bootstrap` (fresh) **or** `npm run upgrade-super-admin` (legacy)
3. Sign in at `/admin` → create review → bootstrap review admin
4. `/admin/{slug}` → project password → upload RIS → create reviewers
5. Share `/r/{slug}` + reviewer credentials only

See [credentials-and-setup.md](./docs/deployment/credentials-and-setup.md).
